SW,<br><br>
Back. Not your fault. I am primed for reasons about which only you are fully aware. Isn't it interesting how this stuff works. Kick me in the ass somewhere, and I go back to 'Nam in my head and come back out rip shit fighting. It must be really confusing and scarey to the uninformed observer. I have very little memory of the last time I really tripped out, and that was some time ago. I was told it was legendary. Thank God I work only on a verbal level. I am in really much better control now. Lots of hard work did that. <br><br>
*There* is a little truth for people to chew upon. That is part of what PTSD is all about. The gift that keeps on giving. Quite a Vietnam War souvineer, huh!.
